{"tid":218078,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8日3劫7仔　越南斧頭賊落網","createTime":"2017-04-26T08:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T09:07:56.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd484a7f57eded8233d3e1e3de2ab55e4c172169","tid":218078,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170426/photo/bkn-20170426164639099-0426_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170426165344\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170426%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170426164639099-0426_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170426165344&h=0a007e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斧頭賊8日内3劫便利店，新界北總區重案組接手跟進，相信3宗案件由同一人所為，經深入調查後，今日拘捕一名39歲越南男子。據悉，他早前提出免遣返聲請獲發「行街紙」留港的假難民。<br />\n<br />\n獨行斧頭賊8日内3劫便利店，第一宗發生於上周二，一名戴鴨舌帽男賊闖入屯門山景邨商場7-11便利店，以斧頭指嚇店員，掠去共8600港元。至本周日，賊人又闖入長沙灣寶熙苑商場7-11便利店，以斧頭指嚇女職員，掠走5800元。在昨日凌晨，旺角界限街一間7-11便利店再遭斧頭賊打劫，擸走5800元現金後逃去。"},{"pid":"3532ff20c2d8750ddcc454d79a27daa841142541","tid":218078,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:57:51.000Z","msg":"幅圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737007521b14e9642fd581cd793045bfe7b98fdd","tid":218078,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"一枝穿雲箭..."},{"pid":"8442ae4ad5dcb6b7242a3a7e52125d9830e9e419","tid":218078,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:07:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}